description: Kaizen Discovery Inc. explores for mineral projects in Peru and Canada. It holds interest in the Pinaya Copper-Gold Project that covers an area of 101 square kilometers and includes 10 kilometers of underexplored strike length within the Andahuaylas-Yauri Porphyry Belt in southeastern Peru. The company is headquartered in Vancouver, Canada. Kaizen Discovery Inc. operates as a subsidiary of HPX TechCo Inc.
